Description_lang: You loot $s1% more Infused Rubies, and dredgers throughout Revendreth offer you an expanded selection of goods.

description_blz.en_US: You loot 20% more Infused Rubies, and dredgers throughout Revendreth offer you an expanded selection of goods.

description_blz.de_DE: Ihr plündert 20% mehr durchflutete Rubine und Gräber in ganz Revendreth bieten Euch eine größere Auswahl an Waren an.

description_blz.ko_KR: 마력 깃든 루비 획득량이 20%만큼 증가합니다. 또한 레벤드레스 전역의 허드레꾼이 판매하는 상품의 폭이 넓어집니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 獲得的灌能紅寶石提高20%，且瑞文崔斯各地的泥掘者會提供你更多樣的貨物選擇。
description_blz.zh_CN: 你可以拾取额外20%的注能红宝石，雷文德斯各处的泥仆会向你提供更多商品。
